11. Mada signifying ‘just now’ or ‘this moment! Modus, as stated above, signifies generally ‘a measure,’ specially it denotes ‘a measure of time,' ‘an unit of time,' and is employed with reference to the unit of time immediately preceding an event ; or, during which an event is taking place3 or, immediately following an event.
